html
	head
		title= "The Hunt"
		script(src="/javascripts/countdown.js")
		script(src="/javascripts/global.js")
		link(rel="icon", href="/images/logo.png")
		script(src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-1.1p.4.js"   integrity="sha256-Qw82+bXyGq6MydymqBxNPYTaUXXq7c8v3CwiYwLLNXU="   crossorigin="anonymous")
		link(rel='stylesheet',href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/css/bootstrap.min.css")
		script(src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.6/js/bootstrap.min.js")
		link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/style.css')
	body
		nav(class="navbar navbar-static-top container-fluid",role="navigation",id="titlebar")
			div(class="navbar-inner container-fluid")
				div(class="navbar-header") 
					a(class="navbar-brand headertext", id="headertext") The Hunt: Boston
				ul(class="nav navbar-nav pull-right")
					li(class="active")
		div(class="jumbotron container-fluid row secondjumbo", id="bigfrontpageimage")
			div(id="explanatorytext")
				h1(class="frontheading",id="frontheading") Boston's only paid scavenger hunt
				b(id="smallheadingtext") The Hunt is a paid scavenger hunt pitting participants against each other in a battle of wits. Participants or teams sign up and pay $2. On hunt day, we send you a text message with the first clue. You have two hours to follow the clues to the ultimate prize.
				b(id="smallheadingtext")  The winning teams gets $100 or 25% of the money paid in and their faces on a billboard in Boston.
				br
				br
				b(id="smallheadingtext") The next hunt is on 
				b(id="smallheadingtext",class="datetext") #{date}. 
				b(id="smallheadingtext") Sign up with your co-workers or friends
		div(class="jumbotron container-fluid row", id="frontpagejumbotron")
				div(class="col-sm-3 text-center")
						img(src="/images/login.png",class="frontpageimage",id="frontpageimage")
						i(id="jumbotext") Sign up for the Hunt in your city by entering an email below
				div(class="col-sm-3 text-center")
						img(src="/images/moneyup.png",class="frontpageimage",id="frontpageimage")
						i(id="jumbotext") If enough people sign up, we'll email asking for $2 and call the hunt on!
				div(class="col-sm-3 text-center")
						img(src="/images/clue.png",class="frontpageimage",id="frontpageimage")
						i(id="jumbotext") You'll receive the first clue via text on Hunt Day (#{date})
				div(class="col-sm-3 text-center")
						img(src="/images/treasure.png",class="frontpageimage",id="frontpageimage")
						i(id="jumbotext") Follow the clues around Boston to the grand prize
		div(class="container-fluid text-center pagination-centered nomarginrow" id="content")
				div(id="countdownholder" class="row")
					div(class="col-sm-4")
						p(id="frontpagecountdowntext" class="lead") The next hunt begins in:
						div(id="countdown", class="green")
					div(class="col-sm-4")
						p(id="frontpagecountdowntext" class="lead") Number of hunters signed up
						div(id="numberhunters",class="green")
							p 52
					div(class="col-sm-4")
						p(id="frontpagecountdowntext" class="lead") Current prize amount
						div(id="prizeamount", class="green")
							p $100
		div(id="hunt-join")
			form(id="form",action="/hunterjoin",method="post",onsubmit="return formvalidation()")
				input(type="text",id="HunterEmail",name="HunterEmail",style="color:#888;", value="Enter your email", onfocus="inputFocus(this)",onblur="inputBlur(this)")
				p(id="errormessageholder")
				div(id="submitbuttonholder")
					button(type="submit",action="post",id="frontpagesubmitbutton",class="submitbutton") I want to participate: here's my email
			
					